Woman dumped her husband's body in a pit and poured concrete under Belgorod
In the Belgorod region, a woman confessed to killing her own husband, whom she dumped in a pit with waste and poured with concrete, according to the website of the regional department of the RF IC.
It is noted that the suspect had been married to the deceased since 1999.
In recent years, the husband began to abuse alcohol and after another quarrel, the woman decided to kill.
"When the spouse fell asleep, the suspect tied his hands and feet, put a plastic bag on his head and pressed a pillow.
When the husband stopped showing signs of life, she wrapped her body in a carpet, carried it out into the yard and hid it in the pit.
The next day I called a concrete mixer and poured a pit with concrete," the department reported.
The woman later reported her husband missing.
Relatives of the deceased appealed to the police, who opened the pit and recovered the body.
The investigation intends to ask the court to arrest the suspect.
The investigation into the criminal case is currently ongoing.
